name: Human Hair Dreadlocks Natural Crocheted
description: I've recently cut off and combed out my well established dreadlocks. They have been well maintained and constantly tightened, only ever washed with natural ingredients and never ever had any parasites or other nasties. I have 11 for sale around 12inches long with loose tips. They are currently a blend of blondes,blues, greens, pinks and purples, I think they look like space lol but obviously being my own hair these can be dyed any colour you like. Perfect for an undercut or extensions for your own dreadlocks. They are quite uniform in thickness, around sharpie thickness and slightly bigger. Any questions or further photos required please message Thank you xx
